title: Oct. 21, 2015 Commonwealth Scholarship Announcement (Government of Grenada)
text: ( Source : Government of Grenada ) ST. GEORGE , GRENADA, OCTOBER 20, 2015 : The Ministry of Education and Human Resource Development hereby informs the public of 75 scholarships from the Indian Technical and Economic Cooperation [ ITEC ]
